---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Garage Cabinet Warranty — 1-Year Limited"
  description="Klovo modular garage cabinet warranty: 1-year limited coverage on defects in materials and workmanship. Coverage details and how to make a claim."
  keywords="garage cabinet warranty, modular garage cabinet warranty, Klovo warranty"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Warranty</span>
      <h1 class="page-h1" style="margin:12px 0 0; max-width:560px;">1 year. <em>Because we mean it.</em></h1>
      <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--muted); font-size:17px; line-height:1.65; margin:16px 0 0; max-width:560px;">
        Every Klovo cabinet is backed by our 1-year limited warranty. We build our cabinets to last decades — and we stand behind what we build.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">

      <div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--display); font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); margin:0 0 12px;">What's Covered</h2>
        <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
          Defects in materials and workmanship under normal residential use. Panel integrity, connector function, hinge mechanisms, drawer slides.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--display); font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); margin:0 0 12px;">What's Not Covered</h2>
        <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
          Normal wear and tear, damage from misuse, commercial use, unauthorized modifications, and damage from exposure to standing water. Our cabinets feature moisture-resistant design with sealed 1mm PVC edgebanding on all exposed edges.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--display); font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); margin:0 0 12px;">How to Make a Claim</h2>
        <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
          Contact <a href="mailto:warranty@klovo.com" style="color:var(--klovo-blue);">warranty@klovo.com</a> with your order number, photos of the issue, and a brief description. Our team will respond within 2 business days.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--neutral); border-radius:10px; padding:28px 32px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--sans); color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:15px; line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
          For full warranty terms and conditions, please contact our support team. Warranty is valid for the original purchaser and begins on the date of purchase. Proof of purchase required for all claims.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
